DIVINE 4.0
==========

Please refer to `doc/manual/building.md` for build instructions.

Reference of commandline options is available with `divine help`, or in the
manual [1]. For an introduction on how to use the tool, please refer to
`doc/manual/using.md`. You can find various example models to try in the
`doc/examples` directory.

Reporting Problems
------------------

Please email us at divine (at) fi.muni.cz if you encounter a problem that you
believe is an error in DIVINE.

Obtaining New Versions
----------------------

The latest release is always available through our homepage [2].

[2]: http://divine.fi.muni.cz/

